1. Take the backup of the PROD database.

bardpbnrduva01 PROD database
--------------------------------------------

/u01/app/scripts/dba-tools/bin/dbbackup.sh db PROD FALSE > /u01/app/scripts/backup/logs/ebs_db_backup_PROD-`date +\%a-\%d-\%b-\%Y-\%H-\%M`.log 2>&1

2. Add READ ACCESS on GENERAL.GOBEACC to the following Oracle Accounts

GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO FINREP;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO STUREP;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO FAIDREP;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO ALUREP;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO DEANREP;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO PAYREP2;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO ZNETCAS;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO ZNETSYS;
GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO MISREP;


3. Validate the grants by executing the following query.

select GRANTEE,OWNER,TABLE_NAME,PRIVILEGE from dba_tab_privs where TABLE_NAME='GOBEACC' and GRANTEE in ('FINREP','STUREP','FAIDREP','ALUREP','DEANREP','PAYREP2','ZNETCAS','ZNETSYS','MISREP');

##################

SQL> GRANT SELECT ON GENERAL.GOBEACC TO FINREP;

Grant succeeded.

